name: Club Prime
Prod_desc: Club Prime from the house of CenturyPly is the only plywood that passes 25 stringent tests as per Bureau of Indian Standards. It's a superior quality all-rounder plywood that comes with revolutionary technologies such as Firewall and ViroKill. Together with being completely waterproof, Club Prime plywood comes with a 25 year warranty against borer and termite attacks, ensuring that your furniture always remains as good as new.
